{"type": "article", "id": 34082, "title": "旅行洗漱用品多？带上这个卷轴就够了｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-03T23:09:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 34601, "name": "山中一宏"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 361, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161103222448muBqChZo5gn6VdLU.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Passage by Kazuhiro Yamanaka</h3><p>日本设计师山中一宏（<a href=\"http://www.kazuhiroyamanaka.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kazuhiro Yamanaka</a>）最近受邀为房产商<a href=\"http://www.mec-r.com/english/\" rel=\"nofollow\">东京三菱地所</a>旗下的房屋进行室内设计，他为此特别创作了这套用网球拍线制作的家具系列 Passage。鉴于拍线本身就相当坚韧，山中直接让它们充当了椅背和座位，确保弹性和耐用。拍线还出现在椅腿和桌腿外，看起来就像是这些家具自带了视觉特效一样。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103175621Xdy5LD98knzM07r6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103175623sH3yUKI9j8lFuMhS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103175623R8uaZrqOtvfEXebm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016110317562340iMwG95lOpTqDQe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103175623kL0DJPdhu1nRlvA2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>DodeCal by Ric Bell</h3><p>很快就要迎来 2017 年，你想过用什么样的日历来装点你的桌面吗？如果你喜欢可以拿在手里把玩的设计，不妨看看英国设计师 Ric Bell 带来的多面体日历 DodeCal。独特的十二面体结构和每一面的文字排布都是 Bell 经过精密计算后设计而成的，每一块都由工匠手工加工之后再采用镭射技术进行雕刻，期间还需要进行人工翻转。目前第一批日历已经售罄，如果你对它感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"http://dodecal.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>进行第二批的预定。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016110317563967YlWefDU2M5O0tL.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.033333\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103175636kfXKFzLJ6A537vxP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103175636k8KpjXcEUvlrhiy2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103175636e7WjC6IxzP3Zgu0n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103175636HxwS51XKcrJo9hv3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>XUBER by Team Xube</h3><p>是不是对带着各种洗浴用品的瓶瓶罐罐到处跑的体验已经有些厌倦了？最近来自新加坡的设计团队带来了一款能够替你省下背包空间的洗浴工具 XUBER。它由四个柱状硅胶容器组合而成，你可以在这些容器里灌上沐浴乳、洗发水等用品，像卷轴一样把它们卷起来装进包里即可。由于它的背面可以不留痕迹地吸附在任何平面上，当你到了浴室只要把它展开贴在墙上即可。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1268071643/xube-streamline-your-shower-experience-on-the-go\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 28 新加坡元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103222247xkNBVm9WYS4IHz73.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103222248CZJsYitV4GN0bUPM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670588\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611032222507TkbEeSWiIXYC1Dt.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611032222479CUDToJStVlxB5K2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.829630\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103222247407ofGMlUKsYT5x9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>HYDE by Danny Venlet</h3><p>          </p><p>在某个位置才亮起的天花板和墙壁听起来是不是有点像科幻电影里的场景？设计师 Danny Venlet 最近发明了一套名为 <a href=\"http://www.kovr.be/\" rel=\"nofollow\">HYDE</a> 的照明系统，尝试将灯饰与建筑元素巧妙地融合在一起。你也可以把它理解为智能建材板，材质、大小以及颜色都可以进行定制。内置的 LED 灯通过配套的应用进行开关、调节明暗等操作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611031858071Ka0unzG5xE6AHIj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.730000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103185808MFUrdgDCZ1Nq2sXR.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.622500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103185807qcWhRlupe9sTrFGb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.450000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103185807y0EDjvHtXKB8rRWN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103185807VDFw307JdkGBqXz4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Entag by Jihoon Suh &amp; Yongdae Kim</h3><p>在办公桌前久坐又不注意姿势很容易影响到脊椎的健康，为了让忙碌的办公族们能够意识到坐姿的重要性，韩国设计师 Jihoon Suh 和 Yongdae Kim 带来了这款名为 <a href=\"http://www.jihoonsuh.com/work#/entag/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Entag</a> 的智能项链。考虑到不少职员会使用门禁卡进出，挂件被设计成了卡套的模样，另一头配备了内置姿势感应器的小方块。一旦它感应到用户的颈椎向前倾，配套的手机应用就会发送提醒。应用界面不仅会直观地显示姿势的倾向，还会告诉你颈椎相应地要承受多少重量。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103182439MPwseGoyOiWN5gm6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.631429\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103182439ytle1cUBVTaAo04F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623810\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611031824414ldwoFk5gE2aTXqD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103182439PYOAsXxKGNTQIURi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103182440ye7aNxksr6Qidw0G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.631429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Aging bottle by Malgorzata Rosolak</h3><p>要了解葡萄酒的年龄，除了看年份做减法之外还能不能变得更有趣呢？瑞士设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/mrosolak\" rel=\"nofollow\">Malgorzata Rosolak</a> 带来的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/36560639/Aging-bottle\" rel=\"nofollow\">Aging bottle</a> 就是一个简单却很讨巧的概念酒瓶：瓶身主要由白色陶瓷制成，底部则是表面涂有促氧化剂的黄铜。根据不同的环境，在两到三年的时间里，你就能看到这一部分慢慢变成了绿色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103175700bnML2JjV9ZaOp56z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.621667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611031757045VRP2b4sWKjX1Nie.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.590833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103175700OTtBvPSj3ZLedCgw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103175700OZpbVT6WUwDeoRuS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103175659E5Rfl2BveLydgbrO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103175701jK2IzQpqeVa5uDC8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}